# Test the "Players" module

Files in this directory are used to test the Players module.

Prerequisites:
  - python3 must be installed (sudo apt-get python3)
  - pip3 must be installed (sudo apt-get install python3-pip)
  - pipenv must be installed (pip3 install pipenv)
  - the 'mongod' service is running, listening to the port 27017

To execute all automated tests, run the following commands from 
within this directory:

$ pipenv install
$ pipenv shell
(test_players)$ python3 -m unittest test_app_players.py
(test_players)$ exit
$ pipenv clean




